42static struct _krb5_key_type keytype_null = {
43 KRB5_ENCTYPE_NULL,
44 "null",
45 0,
46 0,
47 0,
48 NULL,
49 NULL,
50 NULL,
51 NULL,
52 NULL,
53 NULL
54};
55
56static krb5_error_code
57NONE_checksum(krb5_context context,
58 struct _krb5_key_data *key,
59 const void *data,
60 size_t len,
61 unsigned usage,
62 Checksum *C)
63{
64 return 0;
65}
66
67struct _krb5_checksum_type _krb5_checksum_none = {
68 CKSUMTYPE_NONE,
69 "none",
70 1,
71 0,
72 0,
73 NONE_checksum,
74 NULL
75};
76
77static krb5_error_code
78NULL_encrypt(krb5_context context,
79 struct _krb5_key_data *key,
80 void *data,
81 size_t len,
82 krb5_boolean encryptp,
83 int usage,
84 void *ivec)
85{
86 return 0;
87}

89struct _krb5_encryption_type _krb5_enctype_null = {
90 ETYPE_NULL,
91 "null",
92 NULL,
93 1,
94 1,
95 0,
96 &keytype_null,
97 &_krb5_checksum_none,
98 NULL,
99 F_DISABLED,
100 NULL_encrypt,
101 0,
102 NULL
103};
